    <item>
      <title>伊朗革命卫队在霍尔木兹海峡附近扣押集装箱船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-13/urgent-british-military-warns-of-possible-vessel-being-boarded-near-strait-of-hormuz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国迪拜（美联社）——伊朗准军事革命卫队的突击队周六从直升机上垂降到霍尔木兹海峡附近的一艘以色列附属集装箱船上，并扣押了该船，这是两国之间一系列袭击事件中的最新一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-13/urgent-british-military-warns-of-possible-vessel-being-boarded-near-strait-of-hormuz</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 08:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MSC 表示，巴尔的摩灾难中的托运人面临“共同海损”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/baltimore-bridge-companies-with-goods-on-ship-on-the-hook-for-damages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据世界领先的集装箱运输公司称，摧毁巴尔的摩弗朗西斯斯科特基大桥的船主已启动一项正式程序，在受灾大理上拥有货物的公司将不得不分担部分财务损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/baltimore-bridge-companies-with-goods-on-ship-on-the-hook-for-damages</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 07:45:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
